projects.title: Odd Duck Products
projects.description: One of the first apps I was working on in my 201 courses at codefellows. I had to develop an application based on product votes and views. Upon clicking on your favorite product twenty five times it will render and a total. This was a challenging project for we had to use only html, css and javascript. I've learned a lot!
